{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb16d34e31","title":"关启兴的论点","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b599828684","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"cb16d34e31"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"17cd1d629f","name":"关启兴"},{"id":"4e38dc5cec","name":"西北师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7930fd5e65","type":"title","text":"关启兴的论点","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"31cffcfdfd","type":"authors","text":"西北师范学院关启兴","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"cb32ab085a","type":"subtitle","text":"一、关于肃反问题：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"2f0465e3cb","type":"paragraph","text":"1．我不同意毛主席说的成绩是主要的缺点是次要的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"97b9be95b9","type":"paragraph","text":"2．肃反不应该由群众来搞，应该由检查部门来搞，因为有很多群众没有头脑，跟着胡闹。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"d9f07b2098","type":"paragraph","text":"3．由于中央的政策订得模糊，所以犯了很多错误，两个主要错误是：“无的放矢，将错就错”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"49734722a4","type":"subtitle","text":"二、关于社会主义制度问题：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"6e7dfdb2b2","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“我不承认世界只有两条路线，而还有第三条路线”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"91aa04fe67","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“苏联自己处于大国主义地位，各国行事也要看苏联的脸色，我们中国也是这样，中国没有真正的独立”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"d3f163552f","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“不见得社会主义没有缺点，资本主义就不一定没有优点，南斯拉夫脱离苏联这么久，它不是社会主义，也不是资本主义，所以还是有第三条道路可走”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"4f8852264c","type":"subtitle","text":"三、关于马列主义问题：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"e0ceccddd8","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“马列主义不见得是最好的，社会是向前发展的，以后说不定还有比马列主义更好的主义”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"6279ba22b4","type":"appellation","text":"2．我们现在学的不是马列主义，而是苏联主义，因为联系的尽是苏联经验，学习的也是联共党史，故叫“苏联主义”。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"a29efa6026","type":"subtitle","text":"四、关于三害根源：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"47296bae04","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“我不承认中国有宗派主义，各民主党派和共产党并没有墙，墙是不同政治观点产生的，若说有派，只有共产党一派，要拆墙和沟，只有在党的政策上改变，要检查，先从中央检查起从政策和方针来检查，和对待非共产党的政策来检查”。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"af586b7ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“宗派是由于党的政策方面产生的”。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"1a902a7879","type":"subtitle","text":"五、关于对右派的斗争问题：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"6945b4ecc3","type":"paragraph","text":"1．右派的产生是由于肃反的付作用。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"cd9b131875","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“反右派的指示是党还是政府？不是政府，是党，我还认为是宗派”。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"06399069cf","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“奇怪的很，党正在整风，但现在又在反右派，这不是助长了三害吗？你们着，将来还要整群众”。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"459e62745d","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“共产党政策是善变的，整风整到我们头上了，老百姓再整不整”？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"b1d83f26de","type":"subtitle","text":"六、关于整风问题：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"ba16b524b9","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“整风运动是党耍花样”“我怀疑这次整风运动是让反革命大量暴露问题”。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"a458257db3","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“整风运动要搞就搞党中央”。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"6e78b6e482","type":"paragraph","text":"3．同学们贴大字报，他说：“监狱等着你”。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"},{"id":"45705a072b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《香花乎？毒草乎？(2)》（西北师范学院反右斗争委员会，1957年7月6日）。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31"}],"page":{"id":"ef201a06fc","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cb16d34e31","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}